FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781470067
OL,3,C'We don't know why he died': Family's
OL,4,Cplea for answers over Air India crash
OL,6,FJamie's brother Nick said a year on,
OL,7,Fthey still have no answers about his
OL,8,Fdeath. He said:
OL,10,F"It's obviously been a very difficult
OL,11,F12 months for all the family and his
OL,12,Fclose friends.
OL,14,F"It seems like yesterday all this
OL,15,Fhappened, it's gone so fast but
OL,16,Fthere's also been so much to sort out.
OL,18,F"Anniversaries are always difficult
OL,19,Fbut it's a time for us to reflect,
OL,20,Fremember and honour Jamie.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781470067
OL,3,C'We don't know why he died': Family's
OL,4,Cplea for answers over Air India crash
OL,6,F"I think coming to terms with the
OL,7,Fmagnitude of the whole event and
OL,8,Frealising what my brother and all the
OL,9,Fvictims must have gone through in
OL,10,Fthose fatal seconds is horrifying.
OL,12,FHe said: "Also with him going so
OL,13,Fsuddenly and unexpectedly there's been
OL,14,Fso much to sort out, from his house
OL,15,Fand business.
OL,17,F"None of us expected, least of all
OL,18,Fhim, what happened last year.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781470067
OL,3,C'We don't know why he died': Family's
OL,4,Cplea for answers over Air India crash
OL,6,F"I think all the families and
OL,7,Frepresentatives have been pressing for
OL,8,Fmore details on the crash to be
OL,9,Fpublished.
OL,11,F"We got a snippet last July which shed
OL,12,Fa lot of light onto the captain.
OL,14,F"I know how, where and when my brother
OL,15,Fdied but still one year on we don't
OL,16,Fknow why he died.
OL,18,F"We're hoping something materialises
OL,19,Fpretty soon because the investigation
OL,20,Fand its findings have dragged on far
OL,21,Ftoo long now.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781470067
OL,3,C'We don't know why he died': Family's
OL,4,Cplea for answers over Air India crash
OL,6,F"I think, as expected, there's been a
OL,7,Flot of media, written and TV coverage
OL,8,Fof the crash.
OL,10,F"There have been months and months
OL,11,Fthough where there's been little or
OL,12,Fnothing made of such a huge disaster.
OL,14,F"More than 50 British people lost
OL,15,Ftheir lives in one of the most tragic
OL,16,Fcircumstances imaginable in modern
OL,17,Fhistory and for us it's a time to
OL,18,Fremember our loved ones, but it brings
OL,19,Fback so many horrible, traumatic and
OL,20,Fsad memories of 12th June 2025".
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
