PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1781470067
OL,3,C'We don't know why he died': Family's
OL,4,Cplea for answers over Air India crash
OL,6,FA preliminary report into the incident
OL,7,Ffrom India's Aircraft Accident
OL,8,FInvestigation Bureau found both of the
OL,9,Fplane's fuel switches moved to the
OL,10,F"cut-off" position "immediately" after
OL,11,Ftake-off, stopping fuel supply to the
OL,12,Fengine.
OL,14,FA spokesperson for Air India said:
OL,15,F"Air India remains committed to
OL,16,Fsupporting every individual impacted
OL,17,Fby the AI171 tragedy with care and
OL,18,Fcompassion".
